{"tid":2059536,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港版國安法】去信學校警告禁罷課 楊潤雄：教師事假只可用於紅白二事","createTime":"2020-06-11T04:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T08:40:35.000Z","uid":38954,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a192e86c0311614af773d0c9ea68017d09a74c","tid":2059536,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T04:06:16.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄昨向全港中小學校長發信，要求學校阻止師生就反對「港版國安法」參與罷工罷課。楊又要求校方引導學生「理性分析」「港版國安法」，並應阻止學生在校內發起或組織叫口號、組人鏈等行動。楊潤雄今早在電台節目再以反對政治帶入校園為由，重申教育局反對任何形式罷課，又指作為專業教師，不應該罷課，更聲言參與罷課並非教師申請事假的原因，教師只可以用事假處理紅白二事等緊急事務。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄指，教師若突然不回校教書，是紀律問題，校方作為僱主，應按學校程序及僱傭條例去處理，教育局亦會嚴肅跟進；而學生上課最重要是學習，不應浪費時間做「無謂的事」，校方及家長應「勸導學生珍惜時光」，又稱若學生屢勸不改，校方應考慮如何拿捏好「訓輔」的比重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200611/RARXGO447AQDEJITCLXG4UHOFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200611%2FRARXGO447AQDEJITCLXG4UHOFM%2F&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRK%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=3ac2b098\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200611%2FRARXGO447AQDEJITCLXG4UHOFM%2F&h=4d69d4ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200611/RARXGO447AQDEJITCLXG4UHOFM/</a>"},{"pid":"633f70fe0837a6241de5d3ee3d4182e1c05ee8b4","tid":2059536,"uid":273703,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T04:07:30.000Z","msg":"不應政治化學校假期"},{"pid":"0889b1adac754ceba6e16ee46bee36c159bb8588","tid":2059536,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T04:09:33.000Z","msg":"去考車都唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bbc04b7a78c3d7d87db093d72c8c4566691f4a","tid":2059536,"uid":111316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T04:13:33.000Z","msg":"可以幫狗做白事"},{"pid":"e33bcb1f5009d5d